# Project Structure Guide

This is a Visual Asset Library (VAL) project for managing icon sets and sprite sheets. The main components are:

## Core Files
- [index.html](mdc:index.html) - Main portal page with navigation to tools
- [visual-asset-library.html](mdc:visual-asset-library.html) - Interactive icon catalog viewer
- [lou32-asset-assembler.html](mdc:lou32-asset-assembler.html) - Spritesheet assembly utility

## Asset Organization
- `icons/16x16/` - Individual 16x16 pixel icon files
- `atlas/` - Generated sprite sheet atlases in multiple resolutions (16x16, 32x32, 48x48, 64x64)
- Each atlas contains: CSV, JSON, XML metadata and PNG spritesheet

## Utilities
- [Rename-Icons.ps1](mdc:Rename-Icons.ps1) - PowerShell script for batch renaming icons based on JSON configuration

## Key Features
- Interactive icon browsing with filtering and search
- Sprite sheet generation and visualization
- Multiple resolution support
- Metadata-driven asset management